{"tid":1643911,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求下你地 可唔可以幫我手檢舉","createTime":"2019-10-10T10:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:45:20.000Z","uid":163960,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a77876a1b8e8c2f05deeaa6ba50334880a4e2a2e","tid":1643911,"uid":163960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"事源係有一位台灣攝影師同一位台灣model黎左香港私影，聲稱影左一輯國慶特企<br />\n原本見到有台灣人咁關注香港仲為我地出心出力，我係非常開心的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但一㩒入相簿，發現裡面啲相根本唔係想表達支持香港乜乜乜<br />\n裡面有幾張相都係故意<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">賣肉</span></span>的<br />\n點解咁緊張求大家檢舉？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">一、嚴重影響香港女示威者形象<br />\n二、企圖消費呢場運動<br />\n三、比機會藍絲大造文章</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以我懇求大家，幫手檢舉呢個相簿<br />\n<br />\n附一張被刪左既圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TzqhEC6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTzqhEC6.jpg&h=6264f9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左上面呢張特別暴露之外<br />\n仲有其他相係無拉褲鍊的，詳情大家可以自己入去佢相簿到睇<br />\n<br />\n原po：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100000628663052/posts/2686396878057908?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100000628663052%2Fposts%2F2686396878057908%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=N3SWmacea4shigR4hA2Em45RPfZ%2FgKFUZzIsJfjgB6g%3D&h=7faec335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100000628663052/posts/2686396878057908?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ca5ef78786205e67e8dcd9f2ef8306aaab85b002","tid":1643911,"uid":66822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T10:48:11.000Z","msg":"星期五中環快閃 撐被捕保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FoM1jNJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFoM1jNJ.jpg&h=eaa6b73f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7onWS7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7onWS7K.jpg&h=4e446c9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"